<i>noun</i>: 벽난로, 煖爐, 壁煖爐, 난로, 부뚜막, 煖爐, 난로 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>벽난로, 煖爐, 壁煖爐, 난로</dt><br>
<dd>an open recess in a wall at the base of a chimney where a fire can be built</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: fireplace, hearth, open fireplace</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>부뚜막, 煖爐, 난로</dt><br>
<dd>home symbolized as a part of the fireplace</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: hearth, fireside</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
